<h2><span id="(View_-_Edit_Notes_)Notes"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".28View_-_Edit_Notes_.29Notes"><span class="plainlinks" style="float: right; font-size: small">
(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Severe_radioactivity/doc" title="Severe radioactivity/doc"><span title="View user added notes">View</span></a> - <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Severe_radioactivity/doc&amp;action=edit"><span title="Edit user notes">Edit Notes</span></a> )</span>Notes</span></h2>
<ul><li>Adds <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Body_temperature" title="Body temperature">body temperature</a>, adds 1500 when overheating, and 1500 normally.</li>
<li>Character with 10% chance pollutes current tile by one point for each turn. Effect stops when there is thirty points of radiation.</li></ul>
<span class="plainlinks" style="font-size: small"><center>( <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Severe_radioactivity/doc&amp;action=edit"><span title="Edit user notes">Edit Notes</span></a> )</center></span>
</div>
